data.description: Country Living on 1 acre with huge Metal Workshop. 4 bedroom 2 bath home has lots of potential for the investor or the family looking for sweat equity. Large, fenced backyard , and lots of space with the layout of this home. Seller does not pay customary closing costs, title policy,escrow ,survey/transfer fees, or repairs. Proof of funds required on cash transactions. Lender Pre-Approval letter required for financed offers(dated within the last 30 days). Property being sold AS IS WHERE IS. This property may qualify for Seller Financing(Vendee).."Due to condition, the property may have health/safety risk(s). Prior to entry / access, all parties must sign a Hold HarmlessAgreement and the property may only be shown by appointment"
